transcription.text:

Speaker 2: Well, hello.

Speaker 1: How come it's in the chat?

Speaker 2: Okay. Okay. So then after that, we just have to wait for the pharmacy to ship it out,

Speaker 1: and we should be receiving it within the next three to five business days. Okay, Anthony?

Speaker 2: Okay. I have to wait again. Okay.

Speaker 1: Yeah. Okay. Well, you're all set. Have a good rest of your day.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Bye. You're welcome. Bye.
